      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Religious Studies              : A study of the psychological origins of religion, of some aspects of the religious life (e.g. prayer, conversion, mystical experiences), and of some contemporary religious phenomena (e.g. marginal religious groups, the charismatic movement, glossolalia). The views of Freud and Jung are also considered.          </p>

